      <title>ionic01</title>
      <link href="undefined2018/cjevjyr2r000308si08v0df59.html"/>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="ionic教程01"><a href="#ionic教程01" class="headerlink" title="ionic教程01"></a>ionic教程01</h2><h3 id="安装启动阶段"><a href="#安装启动阶段" class="headerlink" title="安装启动阶段"></a>安装启动阶段</h3><p>全局安装ionic<br><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install -g cordova ionic</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>初始化ionic项目, myApp是项目的名字,会生成一个myApp的文件夹,可以进行更改, blank是ionic官方提供的一个模版,一共三个,分别是blank tabs sidemenu,同时可以不指定模版tabs<br><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ionic start myApp blank</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>进入myApp<br><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd myApp</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>然后执行,如下命令,可以shell会自动打开浏览器,每一次的修改,即可自动更新浏览器界面<br><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ionic serve</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><h3 id="初始化一个新的组件"><a href="#初始化一个新的组件" class="headerlink" title="初始化一个新的组件"></a>初始化一个新的组件</h3><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ionic g page second</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="介绍几个ionic功能"><a href="#介绍几个ionic功能" class="headerlink" title="介绍几个ionic功能"></a>介绍几个ionic功能</h3><h4 id="001进入页面首选page"><a href="#001进入页面首选page" class="headerlink" title="001进入页面首选page"></a>001进入页面首选page</h4><p>首先找到<br>D:\myApp\src\app\app.component.ts<br><br>大约在11行, 可以更改进入的页面首选page,<br><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="number">10</span> <span class="keyword">export</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">MyApp</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">11</span> rootPage:any = HomePage;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">12</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">13</span>  <span class="keyword">constructor</span>(platform: Platform, statusBar: StatusBar, splashScreen: SplashScreen) &#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">14</span>    platform.ready().then(<span class="function"><span class="params">()</span> =&gt;</span> &#123;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>在上面的HomePage是引入的<br><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> &#123; HomePage &#125; <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="string">'../pages/home/home'</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>可以进行更改,比如我更改为<br><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="number">11</span> rootPage:any = HomePage;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>这时候的整体ts文件是<br><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> &#123; Component &#125; <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="string">'@angular/core'</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> &#123; Platform &#125; <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="string">'ionic-angular'</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> &#123; StatusBar &#125; <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="string">'@ionic-native/status-bar'</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> &#123; SplashScreen &#125; <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="string">'@ionic-native/splash-screen'</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> &#123; HomePage &#125; <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="string">'../pages/home/home'</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//这里是新引入的页面,也就是通过ionio g page second 初始化的新page</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> &#123; SecondPage&#125; <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="string">'../pages/second/second'</span>;</span><br><span class="line">@Component(&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  templateUrl: <span class="string">'app.html'</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">export</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">MyApp</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  rootPage:any = SecondPage;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">constructor</span>(platform: Platform, statusBar: StatusBar, splashScreen: SplashScreen) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    platform.ready().then(<span class="function"><span class="params">()</span> =&gt;</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="comment">// Okay, so the platform is ready and our plugins are available.</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="comment">// Here you can do any higher level native things you might need.</span></span><br><span class="line">      statusBar.styleDefault();</span><br><span class="line">      splashScreen.hide();</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;);</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><h4 id="002通过button按钮跳转到新page"><a href="#002通过button按钮跳转到新page" class="headerlink" title="002通过button按钮跳转到新page"></a>002通过button按钮跳转到新page</h4><p>首先,需要在home.html(D:\myApp\src\pages\home\home.html)文件里面写上如下,其中第十行,<br>有一个按钮小组件,绑定了click事件,绑定的函数是toPageSecond()<br><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">1<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">ion-header</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">2 <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">ion-navbar</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">3    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">ion-title</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">4      Ionic Blank</span><br><span class="line">5    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">ion-title</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">6  <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">ion-navbar</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">7<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">ion-header</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">ion-content</span> <span class="attr">padding</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">10<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">button</span> <span class="attr">ion-button</span> (<span class="attr">click</span>)=<span class="string">"toPageSecond()"</span>&gt;</span>点我进入第二页<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">button</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">11<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">ion-content</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>这时候就需要去D:\myApp\src\pages\home\home.ts进行书写函数toPageSecond()的功能,<br>我们要实现的功能是点击这个按钮直接跳转到second的page里面,那么我们需要做的是在toPageSecond()中直接使用ionic的路由API</p><h5 id="第一步-必须先引入要跳转的页面"><a href="#第一步-必须先引入要跳转的页面" class="headerlink" title="第一步,必须先引入要跳转的页面"></a>第一步,必须先引入要跳转的页面</h5><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> &#123; Component &#125; <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="string">'@angular/core'</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> &#123; NavController &#125; <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="string">'ionic-angular'</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//第一步,必须先引入要跳转的页面</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> &#123; SecondPage &#125; <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="string">'../second/second'</span>;</span><br><span class="line">@Component(&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  selector: <span class="string">'page-home'</span>,</span><br><span class="line">  templateUrl: <span class="string">'home.html'</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">export</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">HomePage</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">constructor</span>(public navCtrl: NavController) &#123;</span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line"> <span class="comment">//代码跳转逻辑,push函数有两个参数,第一个是页面,第二个是参数</span></span><br><span class="line">  toPageSecond()&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">this</span>.navCtrl.push(SecondPage, &#123;</span><br><span class="line">      id: <span class="string">"123"</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#125;);</span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line">  <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(<span class="number">1</span>);</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="003page跳转传递参数的实现"><a href="#003page跳转传递参数的实现" class="headerlink" title="003page跳转传递参数的实现"></a>003page跳转传递参数的实现</h4><ol><li><p>第一步,先设置好接收的参数,比如在second需要接收参数,那么的话,就需要在<code>D:\myApp\src\pages\second\second.ts</code>这个文件里面设置一个容器用来接收,其中的:id或者:home都是用来接收参数的容器</p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">@IonicPage(&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  name:<span class="string">"second"</span>,</span><br><span class="line">  segment: <span class="string">'second-path/<img class="github-emoji" title="id" alt="id" src="https://assets-cdn.github.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/1f194.png?v8" height="20" width="20">name'</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>第二步,参数的处理, 使用用来接收参数</p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">this</span>.navParams.get(<span class="string">"id"</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">this</span>.navParams.get(<span class="string">"name"</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>第三步,传递参数,home页面是来源页面,那么参数的起点就是home.ts,如下</p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">export</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">HomePage</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">constructor</span>(public navCtrl: NavController) &#123;</span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  toPageSecond()&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">this</span>.navCtrl.push(<span class="string">"second"</span>, &#123;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="comment">//这里就是要传递的参数,可以写多个</span></span><br><span class="line">        id: <span class="number">123</span>,</span><br><span class="line">        name: <span class="string">"小明"</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#125;);</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><h3 id="补充-01找不到模块的问题"><a href="#补充-01找不到模块的问题" class="headerlink" title="补充, 01找不到模块的问题"></a>补充, 01找不到模块的问题</h3><ul><li>Component SecondPage is not part of any NgModule or the module has not been imported into your module.<br>这句话的意思是没有把文件新的page注册到app.module.ts的declarations里面,需要在<code>D:\myApp\src\app\app.module.ts</code> 进行增加,同时注意新page的引入</li><li>Error: No component factory found for SecondPage. Did you add it to @NgModule.entryComponents?<br>这个问题是因为没有在entryComponents里面进行注册造成的,因此也需要在 pp.module.entryComponents,需要在<code>D:\myApp\src\app\app.module.ts</code> 进行增加,同时注意新page的引入<figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> &#123; BrowserModule &#125; <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="string">'@angular/platform-browser'</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> &#123; ErrorHandler, NgModule &#125; <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="string">'@angular/core'</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> &#123; IonicApp, IonicErrorHandler, IonicModule &#125; <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="string">'ionic-angular'</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> &#123; SplashScreen &#125; <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="string">'@ionic-native/splash-screen'</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> &#123; StatusBar &#125; <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="string">'@ionic-native/status-bar'</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> &#123; MyApp &#125; <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="string">'./app.component'</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> &#123; HomePage &#125; <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="string">'../pages/home/home'</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//引入新页面</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> &#123; SecondPage &#125; <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="string">'../pages/second/second'</span>;</span><br><span class="line">@NgModule(&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  declarations: [</span><br><span class="line">    MyApp,</span><br><span class="line">    HomePage,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//注册新page</span></span><br><span class="line">    SecondPage</span><br><span class="line">  ],</span><br><span class="line">  imports: [</span><br><span class="line">    BrowserModule,</span><br><span class="line">    IonicModule.forRoot(MyApp)</span><br><span class="line">  ],</span><br><span class="line">  bootstrap: [IonicApp],</span><br><span class="line">  entryComponents: [</span><br><span class="line">    MyApp,</span><br><span class="line">    HomePage,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 进行注册page</span></span><br><span class="line">    SecondPage</span><br><span class="line">  ],</span><br><span class="line">  providers: [</span><br><span class="line">    StatusBar,</span><br><span class="line">    SplashScreen,</span><br><span class="line">    &#123;<span class="attr">provide</span>: ErrorHandler, <span class="attr">useClass</span>: IonicErrorHandler&#125;</span><br><span class="line">  ]</span><br><span class="line">&#125;)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">export</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">AppModule</span> </span>&#123;&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h3 id="补充-02找不到模块的问题-多次引入模块的问题"><a href="#补充-02找不到模块的问题-多次引入模块的问题" class="headerlink" title="补充, 02找不到模块的问题,多次引入模块的问题"></a>补充, 02找不到模块的问题,多次引入模块的问题</h3><p>Type SecondPage is part of the declarations of 2 modules: AppModule and SecondPageModule! Please consider moving SecondPage to a higher module that imports AppModule and SecondPageModule. You can also create a new NgModule that exports and includes SecondPage then import that NgModule in AppModule and SecondPageModule.<br>当出现这个问题的时候,就是你不但在app.module.ts里面引入了secondpage,同时也在</p><h3 id="最后结束-记得把页面首选page恢复"><a href="#最后结束-记得把页面首选page恢复" class="headerlink" title="最后结束,记得把页面首选page恢复"></a>最后结束,记得把页面首选page恢复</h3>]]></content>
      
      
